woke up on a ship, remembering nothing and apparently being able to do some magic. It appeared the ship had been on the sea for days and no one had seen him. He then got hired, when he persuaded a customer to use the ship he had been on to ship some wares. He then sailed with the ship for a few months, until the ship sank and the survivors had to find something new to do, which - for the tiefling - happened to be adventuring.